data.description: This 4 bedroom 3 full bathroom is in an ideal location, with-in minutes to U.C.F., convenient to S.R. 417, Tech Park and in top rated Seminole County schools. This property features a large eat in kitchen with bar seating open to the living area. Beautiful tile flooring through-out. Plenty of room to spread out in this spacious home. Low maintenance landscape and screened in back porch great for relaxing. Property is equipped with a leased FULL SOLAR SYSTEM was installed 2021, roof replaced 2015, AC Unit was replaced on 2022, water heater is a couple of months old. Couple of blocks from play ground, tennis court and baseball field. Located one minute drive to UCF, near to: Siemens, research park, corporate parks, Oviedo Mall and many more shopping strips. Also close access to highways 408 (East-West Expressway), 417 that will conveniently will take you to International Airport, Amusement Parks such as: Disney, Universal Studios among others; Cape Canaveral, NASA, the beaches and everything else that Central Florida has to offer. Quite and peaceful neighborhood. Schedule your showing today!
